Class ElasticSearch

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2

    public class ElasticSearch
extends android.app.Application
    Created by erin on 11/03/16. This class performs ElasticSearch methods such as saving a user, saving an item, retrieving users and items, searching for things etc. We used HttpURLConnection. This is called by a ton of functions (like most views call some function in here), you can see them all listed below. No functions actually call ElasticSearch directly, rather all the below functions use the controllers (ItemController, UserController, and BidController) and their functions which call ElasticSearch to perform ElasticSearch

    Mar-13-2016 from http://stackoverflow.com/questions/18983185/how-to-create-correct-jsonarray-in-java-using-jsonobject

    Author:
    Adam, Andrew, Erin, Laura, Martina
